16 SECTION 3. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
17 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 707.3 of Title 22, unless there
18 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
19 A. Every subpoena issued on behalf of or by a defendant shall
20 state the name of the court from which it is issued and the title of
